to\": 2113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We will shortly provide news of the outcome of the appeal.\\\"\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the appeal\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it was a clumsy error or a legitimate ploy remains to be seen, but Horrie, the beneficiary from the scandal, insisted the rules are there to be followed.\", \"from\": 2176, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clumsy error\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2205}, {\"ngram\": \"a legitimate ploy\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"Horrie\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"the beneficiary\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"the scandal\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2291}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2379}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivac